            "r2_text": "Best leggings I've owned, hands down! Get them! You won't be sorry! I have told 3 friends so far who have ordered! And… I wore them for 3 days without washing to test roll-down, and they NEVER once moved!",
            "r3_name": "Hannah M.",
            "r3_text": "I am often disappointed by leggings. These are perfect. I have thick legs and a definite mom tummy. These are really comfortable."
          }
